WEBVTT

00:00:02.887 --> 00:00:07.899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:12.499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:13.999
♪By your side once♪

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

00:00:17.075 --> 00:00:21.049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

00:00:21.050 --> 00:00:25.970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

00:00:25.987 --> 00:00:30.699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:35.261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

00:00:35.262 --> 00:00:40.445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

00:00:40.725 --> 00:00:43.074
=Shall We Dance=

00:00:43.075 --> 00:00:46.182
=Episode 22=

00:00:54.980 --> 00:00:56.099
Your Majesty.

00:00:56.100 --> 00:00:57.979
The Grand Princess has
led her personal guards

00:00:57.980 --> 00:01:00.099
and brought most
of the rebel forces under control.

00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:02.140
All surviving rebels have surrendered.

00:01:02.180 --> 00:01:04.139
Only the small band
of suicide soldiers led by Jia Yi

00:01:04.140 --> 00:01:05.780
remains unaccounted for.

00:01:06.780 --> 00:01:08.299
So Your Majesty and the Grand Princess

00:01:08.300 --> 00:01:10.580
had already prepared a defence plan.

00:01:11.980 --> 00:01:14.380
Even if I hadn't
taken you away last night,

00:01:14.550 --> 00:01:16.349
Your Majesty had
already arranged a retreat,

00:01:16.350 --> 00:01:17.390
is that right?

00:01:18.940 --> 00:01:20.060
Yes.

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:23.579
You are indeed
the calculating emperor

00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:25.740
that I once knew.

00:01:26.220 --> 00:01:28.819
If I had struck to kill you,
would I have been

00:01:28.820 --> 00:01:29.499
shot down

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:31.579
by a volley of arrows
from the shadow guards

00:01:31.580 --> 00:01:33.020
trailing behind?

00:01:35.620 --> 00:01:37.100
Believe it or not,

00:01:37.260 --> 00:01:38.860
when you saved me yesterday,

00:01:39.180 --> 00:01:41.060
I had no one by my side.

00:01:42.620 --> 00:01:44.860
You could've died by my hands.

00:01:45.460 --> 00:01:46.940
If I died by your hand,

00:01:47.100 --> 00:01:48.540
I'd have no regrets.

00:01:49.780 --> 00:01:51.340
Of course, I believe even more

00:01:51.660 --> 00:01:53.260
that you would never kill me.

00:01:54.220 --> 00:01:55.380
Why?

00:01:55.540 --> 00:01:57.060
Because you're Xiao Man.

00:01:58.220 --> 00:01:59.540
My Xiao Man.

00:02:07.940 --> 00:02:09.500
Where is the Grand Princess?

00:02:09.620 --> 00:02:12.660
She is waiting for Your Majesty
in the Imperial Study.

00:02:14.550 --> 00:02:15.419
Trust me.

00:02:15.420 --> 00:02:16.980
There's still time.

00:02:18.740 --> 00:02:20.420
Aunt, you've worked hard.

00:02:21.180 --> 00:02:22.780
You've borne so much worry for me.

00:02:23.140 --> 00:02:24.380
We're family.

00:02:25.140 --> 00:02:26.580
No need for formalities.

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:28.499
I didn't do this for you alone.

00:02:28.500 --> 00:02:30.859
I did it for Great Qian

00:02:30.860 --> 00:02:32.060
and its people.

00:02:32.580 --> 00:02:33.860
And also...

00:02:36.420 --> 00:02:37.540
Sun Gong.

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:42.380
I've discovered that Sun Gong
was in close contact with Jia Yi.

00:02:43.580 --> 00:02:47.420
Jia Yi's rebellion is
tied to him without a doubt.

00:02:48.860 --> 00:02:50.900
Let me

00:02:52.112 --> 00:02:53.832
act on Your Majesty's behalf

00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:57.260
and eliminate these traitorous rebels.

00:02:58.260 --> 00:02:59.380
Aunt...

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:03.260
He isn't Sun Gong.

00:03:05.540 --> 00:03:07.900
He's Zhen Muyu,
who disappeared years ago.

00:03:11.020 --> 00:03:12.140
You're saying...

00:03:13.940 --> 00:03:16.300
Sun Gong is Zhen Muyu?

00:03:17.260 --> 00:03:18.380
Yes.

00:03:22.980 --> 00:03:24.100
Aunt...

00:03:24.980 --> 00:03:26.100
Aunt...

00:03:26.580 --> 00:03:27.780
What's wrong?

00:03:29.060 --> 00:03:29.979
Help, hurry!

00:03:29.980 --> 00:03:30.900
Yes!

00:03:31.380 --> 00:03:33.099
I'll leave the rest to you.

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:34.179
Decide for yourself.

00:03:34.180 --> 00:03:34.619
Aunt...

00:03:34.620 --> 00:03:35.460
Grand Princess!

00:03:43.340 --> 00:03:44.459
Report!

00:03:44.460 --> 00:03:45.580
Urgent report!

00:03:46.940 --> 00:03:48.979
Your Majesty, victory at the border!

00:03:48.980 --> 00:03:50.659
General Duanmu joined forces
with the Zhenzhe tribe

00:03:50.660 --> 00:03:52.019
and crushed the foreign army.

00:03:52.020 --> 00:03:54.140
Their commander was
shot dead by Mengmei.

00:03:54.260 --> 00:03:55.380
Good.

00:03:55.500 --> 00:03:57.659
Sun Gong's whereabouts
are unknown after the battle.

00:03:57.660 --> 00:03:58.499
Investigation shows

00:03:58.500 --> 00:03:59.939
Jia Yi and his suicide soldiers

00:03:59.940 --> 00:04:01.779
are hiding in the former Zhen residence.

00:04:01.780 --> 00:04:03.539
Our men have surrounded the place.

00:04:03.540 --> 00:04:04.660
Your Majesty,

00:04:04.940 --> 00:04:06.980
allow me to go
and persuade them to surrender,

00:04:07.340 --> 00:04:09.020
to spare their lives.

00:04:11.780 --> 00:04:13.100
Deliver my decree.

00:04:13.140 --> 00:04:14.619
All troops are to hold position.

00:04:14.620 --> 00:04:16.219
No arrows are to harm Jia Yi.

00:04:16.220 --> 00:04:17.860
I will convince him to surrender.

00:04:18.580 --> 00:04:20.979
Shangguan Qing,
bring the former Xiao troops

00:04:20.980 --> 00:04:22.379
and come with me.

00:04:22.380 --> 00:04:23.500
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:04:28.220 --> 00:04:29.780
(To resolve this hatred,)

00:04:30.060 --> 00:04:31.940
(I must face him myself.)

00:04:54.300 --> 00:04:55.860
Chu Ying, you whelp.

00:04:56.180 --> 00:04:59.260
I've been waiting for you a long time.

00:05:02.140 --> 00:05:03.260
Jia Yi.

00:05:04.420 --> 00:05:05.819
I've long known your true identity

00:05:05.820 --> 00:05:07.540
and all your intentions.

00:05:08.220 --> 00:05:09.979
I don't wish to cross blades with you.

00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:11.100
Silence!

00:05:22.420 --> 00:05:23.740
What a cursed fate...

00:05:29.837 --> 00:05:32.307
(Xiao)

00:05:37.620 --> 00:05:38.419
Soldiers,

00:05:38.420 --> 00:05:39.540
hear me out.

00:05:40.580 --> 00:05:42.739
I am General Xiao Congrong's daughter,

00:05:42.740 --> 00:05:43.980
Zhen Mujun.

00:05:44.740 --> 00:05:45.700
I know

00:05:45.780 --> 00:05:48.740
why you chose to follow my uncle.

00:05:48.860 --> 00:05:50.820
Take a good look at me

00:05:51.420 --> 00:05:53.740
and at the elite soldiers behind me.

00:05:54.180 --> 00:05:56.180
Do you recognise any familiar faces?

00:05:57.100 --> 00:05:59.820
They are all former men
of the Xiao Army.

00:06:00.020 --> 00:06:01.940
Do not turn your blades on one another.

00:06:04.660 --> 00:06:07.099
I am Li Qing,
Deputy General of the Xiao Army.

00:06:07.100 --> 00:06:09.100
I order you to lay down your weapons.

00:06:11.580 --> 00:06:12.339
Chang Hong,

00:06:12.340 --> 00:06:13.339
look at me.

00:06:13.340 --> 00:06:14.059
Come here.

00:06:14.060 --> 00:06:14.739
Han Zhenghao,

00:06:14.740 --> 00:06:15.459
come here.

00:06:15.460 --> 00:06:16.259
Lu Shilei,

00:06:16.260 --> 00:06:17.139
come here.

00:06:17.140 --> 00:06:17.939
Zhao Yongsheng,

00:06:17.940 --> 00:06:18.980
come here.

00:06:19.580 --> 00:06:21.580
I know resentment dwells in your hearts.

00:06:22.180 --> 00:06:23.499
Let go of that hatred.

00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:25.179
You are still the Xiao Army.

00:06:25.180 --> 00:06:27.660
Still Great Qian's most loyal soldiers.

00:06:46.700 --> 00:06:47.820
If any of you..

00:06:49.900 --> 00:06:51.460
wish to surrender,

00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:54.460
step forward.

00:07:04.900 --> 00:07:06.139
The Xiao Army

00:07:06.140 --> 00:07:08.340
swears loyalty to Your Majesty!

00:07:10.460 --> 00:07:11.700
Stand down.

00:07:18.175 --> 00:07:22.082
(Xiao)

00:07:27.820 --> 00:07:29.100
Xiao Man...

00:07:30.140 --> 00:07:32.399
You've truly disappointed me.

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:33.520
Uncle.

00:07:33.940 --> 00:07:35.619
I can't lose Chu Ying,

00:07:35.620 --> 00:07:37.380
and I can't lose you either.

00:07:38.180 --> 00:07:39.299
Both of you

00:07:39.300 --> 00:07:41.660
have been
an inseparable part of my life.

00:07:43.820 --> 00:07:44.940
Jia Yi.

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:48.860
I understand the debt
of a father falls upon the son.

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:52.820
But what lies
between us isn't only hatred.

00:07:53.460 --> 00:07:55.379
I will never forget that

00:07:55.380 --> 00:07:56.499
when I was at my weakest

00:07:56.500 --> 00:07:57.980
and loneliest,

00:07:59.140 --> 00:08:00.860
it was you who protected me,

00:08:01.140 --> 00:08:03.260
who drank poison in my stead.

00:08:05.140 --> 00:08:06.660
You watched me grow up.

00:08:07.220 --> 00:08:09.539
You gave my childhood
a glimmer of light.

00:08:09.540 --> 00:08:11.900
I was never Jia Yi!

00:08:14.875 --> 00:08:17.460
From the age of ten,

00:08:18.380 --> 00:08:20.820
I had only one name.

00:08:21.180 --> 00:08:22.380
Good boy.

00:08:22.580 --> 00:08:24.860
Shall I give you a name?

00:08:25.580 --> 00:08:27.940
Your brother is Zhen Xiujin.

00:08:28.300 --> 00:08:30.300
So you shall be Zhen Xiuyi.

00:08:30.580 --> 00:08:33.500
May you live the rest
of your days in peace and joy.

00:08:35.700 --> 00:08:37.420
Zhen Xiuyi...

00:08:39.940 --> 00:08:41.460
I am of the Zhen clan!

00:08:41.780 --> 00:08:44.019
My name is Zhen Xiuyi!

00:08:44.020 --> 00:08:45.140
Fine!

00:08:45.700 --> 00:08:46.900
Zhen Xiuyi.

00:08:48.380 --> 00:08:50.259
I now have the power

00:08:50.260 --> 00:08:52.260
to clear the Zhen clan's name.

00:08:52.820 --> 00:08:54.780
If you can only let go of this hatred...

00:09:05.700 --> 00:09:06.860
Very well.

00:09:07.980 --> 00:09:09.100
Very well.

00:09:10.620 --> 00:09:12.100
I'll let it go.

00:09:22.780 --> 00:09:23.900
Xiao Man!

00:09:24.020 --> 00:09:25.139
Xiao Man!

00:09:25.140 --> 00:09:26.260
Xiao Man!

00:09:28.340 --> 00:09:29.139
Quick!

00:09:29.140 --> 00:09:30.459
The blade is poisoned.

00:09:30.460 --> 00:09:32.460
Apply the antidote to her wound now!

00:09:42.660 --> 00:09:43.699
Xiao Man!

00:09:43.700 --> 00:09:45.139
Xiao Man!

00:09:45.140 --> 00:09:47.460
I understand my uncle's nature.

00:09:47.620 --> 00:09:49.219
I want to use my own life

00:09:49.220 --> 00:09:51.540
to bring an end to this feud.

00:10:02.580 --> 00:10:03.860
Enough...

00:10:12.420 --> 00:10:13.820
Xiao Man...

00:10:15.860 --> 00:10:18.180
I shall bring no more grievances to you.

00:10:23.540 --> 00:10:24.659
All the grievances...

00:10:24.660 --> 00:10:25.379
Uncle!

00:10:25.380 --> 00:10:26.219
Xiao Man!

00:10:26.220 --> 00:10:28.300
Let them end here with me.

00:10:28.700 --> 00:10:29.580
Xiao Man!

00:10:34.740 --> 00:10:35.659
Uncle!

00:10:35.660 --> 00:10:36.940
Xiao Man!

00:10:38.220 --> 00:10:40.660
Uncle!

00:10:42.340 --> 00:10:44.780
Uncle!

00:10:46.060 --> 00:10:48.179
Uncle!

00:10:48.180 --> 00:10:49.700
Chu Ying.

00:10:50.540 --> 00:10:51.819
You've always wanted to know

00:10:51.820 --> 00:10:53.620
your mother's name.

00:10:54.220 --> 00:10:55.019
Xiao Man's mother

00:10:55.020 --> 00:10:57.500
told me in a letter back then.

00:10:58.260 --> 00:11:00.660
Your mother's name was Ji Zhu'er.

00:11:01.380 --> 00:11:02.740
Thank you, Jia Yi.

00:11:04.500 --> 00:11:06.540
I'll take good care of Xiao Man.

00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:34.580
Brother.

00:11:35.500 --> 00:11:36.620
Sister-in-law.

00:11:37.780 --> 00:11:39.379
I've already slaughtered

00:11:39.380 --> 00:11:41.259
the old officials who fanned the flames

00:11:41.260 --> 00:11:42.980
of the injustice against the Zhen clan.

00:11:43.180 --> 00:11:45.180
I've avenged you both.

00:11:48.220 --> 00:11:49.980
Why won't you answer me?

00:11:51.340 --> 00:11:53.300
Did I do wrong?

00:11:55.460 --> 00:11:56.580
I'm...

00:11:57.660 --> 00:11:59.700
I'm Xiuyi...

00:12:03.420 --> 00:12:05.580
I'm your boy!

00:12:07.060 --> 00:12:09.100
Brother!

00:12:12.180 --> 00:12:17.980
You were my only family!

00:12:28.620 --> 00:12:30.100
Brother!

00:12:30.220 --> 00:12:31.619
Sister-in-law!

00:12:31.620 --> 00:12:34.500
Take me with you!